   More Choices
   In addition to MTD, there are many alternate ways of getting around
   Santa Barbara. Click on any of the links below to view some common
   choices:
     * Amtrak
     * Easy Lift (Provider of dial-a-ride and curb to curb service for
       persons with special needs)
     * Greyhound
     * Santa Barbara Airbus (Bus service to and from LAX)
     * Santa Barbara Airport
     * Santa Barbara Bicycle Coalition (Organization that promotes
       bicycling for safe transportation and recreation in Santa Barbara
       County)
     * Santa Barbara Old Town Trolley (Narrated trolley tours in the Santa
       Barbara area)
     * Traffic Solutions (Division of SB County Association of
       Governments, encouraging alternatives to driving alone.)
     * VISTA Coastal Express (daily service between Ventura and Santa
       Barbara)
